<img src="https://tatviquyen.name.vn/static/c41579e41a294ac21b3066c5f5352fd1/14dee/feature.jpg"/><p>Authentication is the process of identifying users that request access to a system, network, or device. Access control often determines user identity according to credentials like username and password. Other authentication technologies like biometrics and authentication apps are also used to authenticate user identity.</p>
